HEADWORD: Itemize
<hw>I"tem*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To state in
items, or by particulars; to list each item in a collection under
discussion; <as>as, to <ex>itemize</ex> the cost of a
railroad</as>.</def> <mark>[Local, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

